Package: tabular
Title: TFL Rendering for Regulatory Submissions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("Vignesh", "Thanikachalam", email = "about.vignesh@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Native emission of clinical tables, figures, and listings to
    RTF, LaTeX, HTML, PDF, and DOCX from a single dplyr-style API. Handles
    decimal alignment via font metrics, group-aware pagination, page-field
    tokens, and inline markup that survives string operations. Designed
    for CDISC ADaM workflows and FDA/EMA regulatory submissions; replaces
    the tfrmt + r2rtf + flextable + gt stitched-together stack with one
    package per format.
